{"id": "1253761415676825691", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "content": "反擊也是麻煩但又複雜的東西", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:20:15.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:21:07.221000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253761469342945361", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "content": "後期沒回血殘局打反擊很痛苦", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:20:28.053000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253761561919623238", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "content": "前期就是爽爽蹭狂氣", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:20:50.125000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767012728180746", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "反擊就是尷尬東西", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:42:29.699000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767075378237480", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "主要是", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:42:44.636000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767232732008570", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "對面驅散 或者不打你就完事了", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:43:22.152000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767339015409846", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "不然凱刻斯的反擊其實很高", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:43:47.492000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767390383050772", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "但回避性太強", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:43:59.739000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767481399709737", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "就導致他一直很尷尬", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:44:21.439000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767722974580797", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "殘局", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:45:19.035000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767788774948874", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "就", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:45:34.723000+00:00"}
{"id": "1253767841732235264", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "content": "也要他撐得到那時候", "timestamp": "2024-06-21T17:45:47.349000+00:00"}
